@startuml
actor Customer
participant API
participant BookingService
participant AvailabilityService
database DB
Customer -> API: POST /api/bookings/
API -> BookingService: create_request(...)
BookingService -> AvailabilityService: check_overlap(vehicle, range)
AvailabilityService -> DB: SELECT overlapping
DB --> AvailabilityService: rows
AvailabilityService --> BookingService: ok
BookingService -> DB: INSERT booking (PENDING)
BookingService --> API: booking
API --> Customer: 201
@enduml
